                                Download .docx
                            </button>
                            <button type="button">
                                Generate letter
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ol>
                <h2>Next steps</h2>
                <p>
                    The patient should take this letter to the Cost Review office in court. Once there, the patient can either drop the letter off with an administrator for delivery to the judge, or ask to personally deliver the letter to the judge. The goal is for the judge to waive or reduce the patient’s court fees upon reading the letter.
                </p>
